。」及後警司更獲原告一方提供與案中同款鋁梯再作示範，惟三次示範的動作均不同。<br />\n<br />\n另外，莫在庭上自言是本案主要證人，原告一方質疑如此重要的證人，為何會在案發兩個半月後才補錄書面供詞。莫回應指不清楚。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210422/YTXN4CNULJB67LKMZO4YXVWCU4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210422%2FYTXN4CNULJB67LKMZO4YXVWCU4%2F&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=115bc147\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210422%2FYTXN4CNULJB67LKMZO4YXVWCU4%2F&h=38fa63aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210422/YTXN4CNULJB67LKMZO4YXVWCU4/</a>"},{"pid":"ab354ca29daff121343c371a4b9dc2287e513066","tid":2500062,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b12eb4cd9fd7b0c75d93fc75b40e3ab7baf77d","tid":2500062,"uid":146351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:31:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYocBqv2ubpXejcSzgF1WPRtdBtUz4GLmu1N7QNYyGoXM?filename=sw4fhD8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsw4fhD8.gif&h=d5cdd695&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}